divs: Sighting DetailsI woke up at approx. 430 in the AM which is very odd for me seeing as I am avery heavy sleeper. I looked out of my window and to the SE I saw the ufo. Itwas a single light that would pulse white, then orange, then white, then orange,ect. It appeared to bounce, almost, back and forth, back and forth. It was veryodd indeed. I observed this light for about 5-8 secounds then expirencedoverwelming tiredness. I then was back to a deep sleep almost instinly.
Summary: light that flashed from white to orange from white
